quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,(Allāhu búra pẹ̀lú) àpáta Tūr
  52,2,(Ó tún búra pẹ̀lú) Tírà tí wọ́n kọ sílẹ̀
  52,3,sínú tákàdá tí wọ́n tẹ́ sílẹ̀
  52,4,(Ó tún búra pẹ̀lú) Ilé Àbẹ̀wò náà
  52,5,"(Ó tún búra pẹ̀lú) àjà tí wọ́n gbé sókè (ìyẹn, sánmọ̀)"
  52,6,(Ó tún búra pẹ̀lú) agbami odò iná
  52,7,Dájúdájú ìyà Olúwa rẹ máa ṣẹlẹ̀
  52,8,Kò sí olùdènà kan fún un
  52,9,(Ó máa ṣẹlẹ̀) ní ọjọ́ tí sánmọ̀ máa mì tìtì tààrà
  52,10,Àwọn àpáta sì máa rìn lọ tààrà (bí eruku àfẹ́dànù)
  52,11,"Ní ọjọ́ yẹn, ègbé ni fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́"
  52,12,"àwọn tí wọ́n wà nínú ìsọkúsọ, tí wọ́n ń ṣeré"
  52,13,(Rántí) ọjọ́ tí wọn yóò tì wọ́n lọ́ sínú iná Jahanamọ ní ìtìkutì
  52,14,Èyí ni Iná náà tí ẹ̀ ń pè nírọ́
  52,15,Ṣé idán ni èyí ni tàbí ẹ ò ríran
  52,16,"Ẹ wọ inú rẹ̀ lọ. Ẹ fara dà á tàbí ẹ ò fara dà á, bákan náà ni fun yín. Ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́ ni A óò fi san yín ní ẹ̀san"
  52,17,Dájúdájú àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu) máa wà nínú àwọn Ọgbà àti ìdẹ̀ra
  52,18,Wọn yóò máa jẹ ìgbádùn pẹ̀lú ohun tí Olúwa wọn fún wọn. Àti pé (Allāhu) yóò ṣọ́ wọn nínú ìyà iná Jẹhīm
  52,19,"Ẹ máa jẹ, ẹ máa mu ní gbẹdẹmukẹ nítorí ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́"
  52,20,Wọn yóò rọ̀gbọ̀kú sórí àwọn ibùsùn tí wọ́n tò ní ọ̀wọ̀ọ̀wọ́. A sì máa fún wọn ní àwọn ìyàwó ẹlẹ́yinjú ẹgẹ́
  52,21,"Àti pé àwọn t’ó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí àwọn àrọ́mọdọ́mọ wọn tún tẹ̀lé wọn nínú ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo, A máa da àwọn àrọ́mọdọ́mọ wọn pọ̀ mọ́ wọn. A ò sì níí dín kiní kan kù nínú iṣẹ́ wọn. Ẹnì kọ̀ọ̀kan ni onídùúró fún ohun t’ó ṣe níṣẹ́"
  52,22,A máa fún wọn ní àlékún èso àti ẹran tí wọ́n nífẹ̀ẹ́ sí
  52,23,Wọn yó sì máa gba ife ọtí mu láààrin ara wọn nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra. Kò sí ọ̀rọ̀ ìsọkúsọ àti ìwà ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra
  52,24,Àwọn ọmọ-ọ̀dọ̀ wọn yó sì máa lọ bọ̀ láààrin wọn. (Wọ́n) dà bí àlúùúlù àfipamọ́
  52,25,"Apá kan wọn yóò dojú kọ apá kan, wọn yó sì máa bèèrè ọ̀rọ̀ lọ́wọ́ ara wọn"
  52,26,"Wọn yóò sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀ àwa jẹ́ olùpáyà láààrin àwọn ènìyàn wa"
  52,27,Ṣùgbọ́n Allāhu ṣàánú wa. Ó sì là wá níbi ìyà Iná
  52,28,"Dájúdájú àwa máa ń pè É tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Olóore, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"